### chainAsync

Chains asynchronous functions.

Loop through an array of functions containing asynchronous events, calling `next` when each asynchronous event has completed.

```js
const chainAsync = fns => {
  let curr = 0;
  const next = () => fns[curr++](next);
  next();
};
```

